n%20the%20seventh%20grade%2C%20according%20to%20the%20series.%20As%20a%20youth%2C%20he%20danced%20and%20shined%20shoes%20for%20money.%20But%20at%20times%2C%20the%20series%20detailed%2C%20Brown%20looked%20to%20more%20unscrupulous%20ways%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20and%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20to%20breaking%20into%20a%20car%20as%20a%20teen.%20The%20performer%20also%20grew%20up%20in%20an%20abusive%20household%2C%20and%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20the%20series%20noted%20that%20abuse%20manifested%20itself%20in%20the%20celebrity's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fslate.com%2Fculture%2F2014%2F09%2Fcold-sweat-my-father-james-brown-and-me-excerpt-james-brown-s-daughter-yamma-brown-reflects-on-growing-up-with-domestic-violence.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epersonal%20and%20professional%20relationships%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20violence%20riddled%20the%20performer%E2%80%99s%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20series%20premiere%2C%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20Brown%E2%80%99s%20daughters%2C%20Yamma%20Brown%20and%20Deanna%20Brown%20Thomas%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eabout%20the%20life%20and%20legacy%20of%20a%20man%20they%E2%80%99ve%20known%20so%20intimately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20interview%20was%20edited%20for%20brevity%20and%20clarity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsEkkZ2rzIW4%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Sneak%20Peek%3A%20Documentary%20Event%20%26quot%3BJames%20Brown%3A%20Say%20It%20Loud%26quot%3B%20Premieres%202%2F19%20and%202%2F20%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20Insider%3A%20Who%20was%20James%20Brown%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYamma%20Brown%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EJames%20Brown%20was%20daddy.%20He%20wasn't%20James%20Brown%20to%20us.%20We%20didn't%20go%20around%20the%20house%20calling%20him%20'James%20Brown.'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeanna%20Brown%20Thomas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20He%20was%20two%20things%20to%20me%3A%20He%20became%20my%20boss%20when%20I%20had%20to%20work%20for%20him%2C%20which%20probably%20was%20harder%20than%20just%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98Daddy.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20the%20experience%20of%20having%20a%20larger-than-life%20celebrity%20dad%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDBT%3A%20It%20was%20one%20thing%20to%20have%20a%20larger-than-life%20celebrity%20parent%2C%20but%20our%20dad%20was%20James%20Brown.%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20that%20Paris%20%5BJackson%5D%20might%20have%20had%20a%20spectacular%20life%20%5Bwith%5D%20her%20daddy%20being%20Michael%20Jackson%2C%20but%20James%20Brown%3F%20It's%20a%20different%20get-down.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20would%20always%20tell%20me%20and%20Yama%2C%20%E2%80%9CY'all%20will%20never%20know%20what%20it%20was%20like%20for%20me%20when%20I%20was%20growing%20up%20because%20you're%20born%20in%5Bto%5D%20royalty.%20You%20have%20everything%20for%20you.%20I%20didn't%20have%20running%20water%2C%20food%2C%20clothes%2C%20and%20education%3B%20a%20nurturing%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYB%3A%20He%20%E2%80%A6%20was%20also%20a%20celebrity%E2%80%99s%20celebrity.%20And%20so%20it's%20interesting%20being%20in%20those%20spaces%20where%20people%20like%20Denzel%20Washington%20are%20coming%20to%20Dad's%20concert%20because%20they%20want%20to%20meet%20him.%20That%20puts%20things%20more%20into%20perspective%20of%20who%20he%20is%20and%20who%20he%20always%20will%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAs%20kids%2C%20I%20imagine%20that%20you%20are%20in%20your%20own%20bubble.%20What%20was%20the%20point%20when%20it%20clicked%20that%20your%20dad%20was%20an%20icon%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYB%3A%20It%20definitely%20didn't%20click%20for%20me%20until%20high%20school%20and%20even%20more%20so%20when%20I%20was%20able%20to%20travel%20with%20him%20outside%20of%20the%20country.%20I%20was%2021%20and%20in%20Paris%20and%20experiencing%20the%20paparazzi.%20It%20just%20puts%20you%20in%20a%20whole%20different%20space.%20%E2%80%A6You're%20just%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20believe%20this%20is%20his%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDBT%3A%20I%20was%20a%20sophomore%20in%20college%2C%20and%20for%20me%20that%20was%20around%2019-20.%20I%20was%20in%20the%20library%20doing%20a%20research%20paper%20and%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet%20me%20check%20out%20what%20they%E2%80%99ve%20got%20on%20Dad%20in%20the%20encyclopedias.%26quot%3B%20And%20as%20I'm%20reading%2C%20I%20see%20our%20names.%20That%20freaked%20me%20out%20because%20I%20expected%20to%20see%20his%20name%2C%20but%20they%20knew%20who%20%3Cem%3Ewe%3C%2Fem%3E%20were.%20This%20is%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22James%20Brown%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20an%20American%20flag.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d35bc1a3bd891424f85fb6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221312%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJames%20Brown%20performs%20during%20United%20We%20Stand%20Concert%20-%20Show%20at%20RFK%20Stadium%20in%20Washington%20DC%2C%20United%20States.%3Cp%3EKMazur%2FWireImage%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYour%20father%20once%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20born%20dead%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20make%20a%20life%20for%20myself.%26quot%3B%20Indeed%2C%20he%20made%20a%20life%20for%20himself.%20He%20owned%20multiple%20radio%20stations%2C%20owned%20his%20masters%2C%20and%20was%20very%20much%20a%20businessman.%20Your%20father%20had%20an%20immensely%20strong%20business%20acumen.%20What%20did%20that%20teach%20you%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDBT%3A%20I%20was%20able%20to%20travel%20around%20the%20world%20with%20Dad%2C%20and%20work%20under%20him%2C%20and%20watch%20him%20before%20he%20got%20to%20the%20stage.%20And%20seeing%20a%20man%20who%20went%20as%20far%20as%20seventh%20grade%20be%20able%20to%20do%20what%20he%20did%E2%80%94I%20mean%2C%20he's%20a%20conglomerate.%20But%20just%20think%20of%20where%20he%20came%20from%20and%20to%20have%20the%20acumen%20like%20you%20speak%20of%2C%20with%20no%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20an%20interview%20one%20time.%20They%20asked%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhere%20does%20all%20of%20this%20come%20from%3F%E2%80%9D%20His%20answer%20was%20God.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CGod%20gave%20me%20everything%20I%20had.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20thing%20that%20the%20documentary%20really%20spoke%20to%20was%20how%20your%20dad%20kept%20a%20tight%20ship%20during%20performances.%20Members%20of%20his%20band%20got%20fined%20for%20missing%20notes%20during%20rehearsal.%20Did%20that%20tough%20approach%20translate%20into%20his%20parenting%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYB%3A%20He%20was%20tired%20by%20the%20time%20he%20came%20home%20(%3Cem%3Elaughs%3C%2Fem%3E).%20But%20let%20me%20tell%20you%20something%3A%20there%20were%20no%20jeans%E2%80%94no%20jeans%20going%20out%20because%20he%20was%20going%20to%20look%20through%20you.%20He%20would%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20who%20you%20think%20you're%20going%20with%2C%20but%20you're%20not%20riding%20with%20me%20looking%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%20He%20was%20impeccable%20with%20the%20dressing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDBT%3A%20He%20was%20also%20very%20strict%20with%20education.%20Of%20course%20us%20going%20to%20school%20was%20very%20important%20and%20he%20always%20wanted%20you%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bnice%20young%20ladies.%26quot%3B%20The%20thumb%20was%20on%20you%20and%20you%20couldn't%20move%20sideways.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yamma%20Brown%2C%20Deanna%20Brown%20Thomas%2C%20and%20Rev.%20Al%20Sharpton%20speak%20onstage%20during%20A%26amp%3BE's%20%26quot%3BJames%20Brown%3A%20Say%20It%20Loud%26quot%3B%20NYC%20Premiere%20Event%20at%20The%20Apollo's%20Vi