onship%2C%20which%20would%20last%20until%20the%20celebrated%20author's%20death%20at%20age%2059%20in%201984.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20reality%2C%20however%2C%20Capote%20and%20O'Shea%20%E2%80%94%20whom%20Capote%20remodeled%20into%20Katy%20Harrington%20%E2%80%94%20began%20their%20relationship%20under%20slightly%20different%20circumstances.%20Here's%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20O'Shea%2FHarrington%20and%20where%20she%20is%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETruman%20Capote%20treated%20Katy%20Harrington%20as%20his%20adoptive%20daughter%20and%20prot%C3%A9g%C3%A9%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kate%20Harrington%20and%20Truman%20Capote%20in%201977.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce31156fcb546d2d501801%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222135%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKate%20Harrington%20and%20Truman%20Capote%20in%201977.%3Cp%3ERon%20Galella%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHarrington%20opened%20up%20about%20her%20relationship%20with%20Capote%20on%20camera%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Capote%20Tapes%2C%26quot%3B%20a%202019%20documentary%20film%20that%20explores%20Capote's%20final%20years%20and%20what%20became%20of%20his%20unfinished%20last%20novel%2C%20%26quot%3BAnswered%20Prayers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20recalled%20she%20met%20Capote%20for%20the%20first%20time%20when%20she%20was%2013%20in%20her%20family%20living%20room%20after%20her%20father%2C%20a%20former%20bank%20manager%2C%20invited%20the%20%26quot%3BIn%20Cold%20Blood%26quot%3B%20author%20over%20for%20dinner.%20What%20she%20didn't%20know%20at%20the%20time%20but%20would%20come%20to%20realize%20was%20that%20the%20two%20were%20lovers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Harrington's%20father%20abandoned%20the%20family%20to%20be%20with%20Capote%20%E2%80%94%20and%20eventually%20abandoned%20the%20writer%20when%20their%20relationship%20had%20run%20its%20course%20%E2%80%94%20the%20teenager%20decided%20to%20call%20Capote%20to%20see%20if%20he%20could%20help%20her%20find%20a%20job.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Capote's%20blessing%20and%20careful%20instructions%2C%20she%20made%20her%20way%20to%20his%20Manhattan%20apartment%2C%20where%20he%20informed%20her%20that%20modeling%20was%20the%20best%20way%20to%20make%20money%20at%20her%20age.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECapote%20helped%20get%20her%20sign%20to%20Wilhelmina%20Cooper's%20model%20agency%20under%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BKaty%20Harrington%26quot%3B%20since%20there%20was%20another%20girl%20with%20her%20same%20name%20on%20the%20books.%20According%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fbooks%2Fwhat-to-read%2Ftruman-capote-pygmalion-tiny-terror-threw-adopted-daughter-high%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kate%20was%20chosen%20as%20it%20was%20one%20of%20her%20grandmother's%20names%2C%20while%20Harrington%20was%20her%20mother's%20maiden%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Gerald%20Clarke%20posited%20in%20his%201988%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dd6f2f6431c6e04a19377d4fda3d500c95a8a2bec4604c472f8b4cfca2a7afad9%26postID%3D65ce2bf4e315c04c5d9d49de%26postSlug%3Dfeud-capote-vs-swans-what-happened-adoptive-daughter-kate-harrington-2024-2%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.co.uk%252FCapote-Biography-Gerald-Clarke%252Fdp%252F0349105456%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiography%20of%20Capote%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20might%20have%20been%20an%20ulterior%20motive%20in%20the%20decision%20to%20change%20her%20name.%20He%20writes%20that%20Capote%20%26quot%3Bassumed%20John's%20place%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20father%20figure%20in%20her%20life%20and%20%26quot%3Berased%20John's%20name%20from%20his%20favorite%20child%26quot%3B%20to%20get%20back%20at%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHarrington%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebecame%20a%20permanent%20fixture%20on%20the%20New%20York%20social%20scene%