Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20also%20sought%20to%20prevent%20Russia%20from%20obtaining%20high-tech%20components%20it%20uses%20to%20build%20weapons%2C%20including%20cruise%20missiles.%20But%20an%20illicit%20trade%20in%20the%20parts%20has%20sprung%20up%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-how-russia-gets-us-tech-cruise-missiles-despite-sanctions-2023-8%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallowing%20them%20to%20be%20imported%20via%20neighboring%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20networks%20of%20shell%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutin%20has%20placed%20the%20Russian%20economy%20on%20a%20war%20footing%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarnegieendowment.org%2Fpolitika%2F90753%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%206%25%20of%20GDP%20spent%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20production%2C%20meaning%20that%20US%20attempts%20to%20seriously%20constrict%20Russian%20weapons%20production%20have%20failed.%20Russia%20is%20now%20producing%20more%20ammo%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Ukraine's%20supply%20is%20running%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20on%20Friday%20pointed%20to%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20invasion%20on%20Russia%20and%20said%20the%20country%20had%20already%20suffered%20%26quot%3Ba%20hell%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20consequences%26quot%3B%20since%20he%20made%20his%20pledge%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWestern%20weapons%20have%20proven%20vital%20for%20Ukraine%20in%20reversing%20Russian%20successes%20in%20the%20early%20weeks%20of%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20could%20soon%20change.%20The%20future%20of%20US%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%20is%20under%20threat%2C%20with%20congressional%20Republicans%2C%20egged%20on%20by%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20opposing%20a%20new%20bill%20that%20includes%20%2460%20billion%20in%20assistance%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20prospect%20of%20more%20sanctions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20limited%20impact%2C%20could%20more%20sanctions%20be%20the%20answer%3F%3C%2