2C%20too.%20Studies%20show%20that%20a%20happy%20relationship%20can%20help%20you%20live%20longer%2C%20from%20boosting%20your%20immune%20system%20to%20even%20dulling%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you're%20in%20a%20good%20relationship%2C%20you%20feel%20hopeful%20about%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cedu.niu.edu%2Fcahe%2Fabout%2Ffaculty%2Fsuzanne-degges-white.shtml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESuzanne%20Degges-White%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20licensed%20counselor%20and%20professor%20at%20Northern%20Illinois%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20She%20said%20this%20hopefulness%20and%20excitement%20can%20translate%20to%20physical%20and%20emotional%20benefits%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDegges-White%20shared%20a%20few%20telltale%20signs%20that%20your%20romantic%20relationship%20not%20only%20feels%20good%2C%20but%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20good%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Your%20body%20feels%20relaxed%20around%20your%20partner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20if%20a%20relationship%20is%20good%20for%20you%2C%20Degges-White%20said%20a%20great%20barometer%20is%20your%20level%20of%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we're%20with%20someone%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20around%2C%20our%20body's%20tense%20and%20we%20may%20not%20notice%20it%20until%20we're%20out%20of%20their%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20opposite%20is%20true%20for%20someone%20you%20feel%20good%20around.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20think%20about%20the%20people%20we%20care%20about%2C%20we%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20expansion%20and%20warmth%20in%20our%20bodies%2C%E2%80%9D%20Degges-White%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20a%20partner%20who%E2%80%99s%20healthy%20for%20you%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20to%20be%20in%20the%20room%20for%20you%20to%20feel%20calmer.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20think%20about%20someone%20smiling%20at%20you%20right%20now%2C%20your%20lips%20maybe%20going%20up%20into%20that%20automatic%20reflex%20smile%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20when%20people%20smile%20at%20us%2C%20we%20smile.%E2%80%9D%20If%20thinking%20of%20your%20loved%20one%20smiling%20makes%20you%20grin%2C%20she%20said%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20solid%20sign%20that%20you%20genuinely%20feel%20connected%20and%20safe%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20You%E2%80%99re%20more%20energized%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDegges-White%20said%20that%20when%20you%E2%80%99re%20in%20a%20bad%20relationship%2C%20your%20body%20can%20feel%20lethargic%20%E2%80%94%20like%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20energy%20to%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%E2%80%9Cwhen%20you're%20in%20a%20healthy%20relationship%2C%20you%20feel%20capable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20feel%20like%20you%20can%20take%20on%20the%20world%20because%20you%20feel%20like%20there's%20a%20lightness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaughing%20and%20talking%20to%20people%20you%20love%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fi-dont-want-to-do-anything%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eknown%20energy%20boosters%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20in%20a%20relationship%20that%20feels%20stable%20and%20fun%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20likely%20to%20feel%20more%20ready%20to%20take%20on%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20You%20adopt%20new%20healthy%20habits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20interesting%20side-effect%20of%20a%20healthy%20relationship%20is%20that%20it%20can%20encourage%20you%20to%20prioritize%20your%20health%20in%20other%20areas%2C%20according%20to%20Degges-White.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20a%20healthy%20relationship%20makes%20us%20more%20energetic%20and%20optimistic%2C%20it%20makes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquick-life-hacks-increase-longevity-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eadopting%20incremental%20healthy%20habits%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20little%20easier.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20our%20relationships%20are%20going%20well%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20our%20life%20will%20usually%20follow%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe're%20thinking%20about%20the%20choices%20we're%20making%2C%20with%20exercise%2C%20with%20diet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20mean%20you%20have%20to%20run%20a%20marathon%20or%20be%20a%20super%20athlete%20as%20proof%20of%20a%20healthy%20bond.%20But%20you%20might%20be%20more%20willing%20to%20take%20a%20walk%20or%20bike%20ride%20if%20a%20partner%20you%20love%20wants%20to%20go%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20more%20that%20sense%20of%20being%20ready%20and%20capable%20and%20able%20to%20do%20these%20things%20and%20to%20want%20to%20do%20these%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-mature-relationship-improving-health-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708346282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cbb59294aa8ee8e84acea5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-mature-relationship-improving-health-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20mature%20relationship%20can%20improve%20your%20physical%20health%20and%20help%20you%20live%20longer.%20Here%20are%20some%20signs%20your%20relationship%20is%20good%20for%20your%20wellbeing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpugachevsky%40insider.com%20(Julia%20Pugachevsky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-mature-relationship-improving-health-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Goldman%20raises%20global%20equities%20to%20'overweight'%20on%20economic%20growth%20prospects%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708346187000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsm