p%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20somebody%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20America%20but%20not%20as%20an%20American%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20things%20that%20maybe%20Americans%20consider%20freedom%20are%20not%20things%20that%20I%20consider%20to%20be%20freedom.%20I%20feel%20Japan%20gives%20me%20the%20freedom%20that%20I%20want%20at%20a%20very%20attractive%20price%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20needing%20to%20drive%20to%20do%20the%20most%20basic%20things.%20Affordable%20healthcare.%20Being%20able%20to%20buy%20alcohol%2024%20hours%20a%20day%20%E2%80%94%20in%20Georgia%2C%20you%20have%20dumb%20blue%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20guns%20and%20violence%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20things%20about%20Japan.%20If%20you%20watch%20Japanese%20news%2C%20nothing%20ever%20happens.%20They'll%20cover%20domestic%20gossip%20as%20news%20and%20they%20have%20feel-good%20stories%2C%20but%20unless%20a%20disaster%20happens%2C%20you're%20not%20necessarily%20hearing%20about%20shootings%20or%20gang%20violence%20or%20anything%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20temple%20that%20I%20walk%20by%20every%20time%20I%20go%20to%20the%20convenience%20store%2C%20or%20I%20can%20take%20a%20different%20path%20and%20go%20through%20a%20bamboo%20forest%20and%20see%20old%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Green%20fields%20in%20a%20rural%20neighborhood%20in%20Japan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cfabdbf533b039a884bdb2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20scenery%20in%20Watson's%20neighborhood.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ned%20Watson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20true%20for%20most%20people%20who%20live%20in%20the%20countryside.%20You%20get%20to%20see%20how%20nature%20works.%20But%20I%20also%20get%20to%20do%20that%20in%20a%20way%20where%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20not%20destroying%20nature%20by%20driving%20a%20big%20old%20truck%20around%20in%20it.%20I%20can%20walk%20through%20it%20and%20see%20little%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20certain%20flowers%20start%20to%20bloom%2C%20you're%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20it's%20this%20season%2C%26quot%3B%20or%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20weather%20is%20going%20to%20start%20being%20good.%26quot%3B%20I%20get%20to%20watch%20rice%20grow%2C%20which%20is%20kind%20of%20boring%2C%20but%20also%20nice.%20I%20get%20to%20see%20the%20birds%20fly%20around%20in%20it.%20I%20don't%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20get%20to%20experience%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20I%20live%2C%20I%20can%20just%20ignore%20the%20outside%20world%20and%20focus%20on%20what%20makes%20me%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20house%20was%20abandoned%20for%20two%20years%2C%20but%20didn't%20need%20much%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20living%20in%20Japan%20since%202010%2C%20and%20I%20got%20this%20house%20in%20late%202019.%20Before%20I%20moved%20to%20Japan%2C%20I%20was%20living%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20a%20home%20in%20Japan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cfab15f533b039a884bce6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221407%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWatson%20paid%20less%20than%20%2445%2C000%20for%20his%20home%20in%20Japan.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ned%20Watson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20onto%20a%20Japanese%20real-estate%20site%20here%2C%20and%20they%20all%20basically%20have%20access%20to%20the%20same%20database.%20I%20set%20up%20the%20criteria%20that%20I%20wanted%3A%20less%20than%2010%20million%20yen%20(or%20%2466%2C696)%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20to%20Tokyo%20Station%20within%2090%20minutes%20by%20train%2C%20more%20than%20400%20square%20meters%20of%20land%2C%20and%20within%20a%2015-minute%20walk%20to%20a%20train%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20as%20much%20land%20as%20possible%20simply%20because%20they're%20not%20making%20any%20more%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20in%20a%20little%20town%20called%20Shisui%2C%20which%20is%20in%20Chiba%20Prefecture.%20I'm%20right%20on%20the%20border%20of%20Narita%20City%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20major%20international%20airports.%20My%20house%20was%206.6%20million%20yen%20(or%20%2443%2C941).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20neighbors%20said%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20came%20to%20look%20at%20it%2C%20but%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20I'm%20the%20one%20who%20ended%20up%20buying%20it.%20The%20house%20had%20been%20unoccupied%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20think%20about%20how%20Japanese%20people%20would%20buy%20property%2C%20anybody%20who%20would%20have%20enough%20cash%20to%20buy%20a%20property%20like%20this%20outright%20would%20probably%20just%20prefer%20to%20get%20a%20loan%20and%20have%20a%20new%20house%20built%20somewhere.%20Unless%20they%20specifically%20wanted%20to%20tear%20this%20place%20down%20and%20live%20on%20this%20land%2C%20there%20is%20not%20much%20incentive%20for%20them%20to%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20typhoon%20earlier%20that%20year%2C%20which%20made%20a%20huge%20landslide%20behind%20this%20house%2C%20so%20that%20probably%20turned%20people%20off%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBecause%20of%20the%20favorable%20exchange%20rate%2C%20everything%20in%20Japan%20is%20cheaper%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20utilities%20in%20Japan%20may%20be%20a%20bit%20more%20overpriced%20than%20the%20US%20just%20because%20of%20Japan's%20electric%20production.%20Because%20they%20shut%20down%20the%20nuclear%20reactors%2C%20they%20have%20to%20import%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20electricity%20bill%20is%20a%20bit%20higher%20than%20most%2C%20but%20I%20also%20use%20a%20lot%20of%20electricity.%20But%20with%20the%20exchange%20rate%20being%20what%20it%20is%20right%20now%2C%20Japan%20is%20basically%2030%25%20cheaper%20price-wise.%20The%20value%20you%20get%20for%20your%20dollar%20over%20here%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20it's%20just%20going%20to%20keep%20getting%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20go%20to%20McDonald's%2C%20you'll%20probably%20get%20the%20best%20McDonald's%20that%20you'll%20ever%20have%20%E2%80%94%20just%20clean%2C%20fast%2C%20and%20really%20looks%20like%20the%20picture.%20A%20Big%20Mac%20right%20now%2C%20I%20think%2C%20is%20480%20yen%2C%20which%20is%20about%20%243.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20having%20a%20mortgage%20or%20rent%20is%20such%20a%20huge%20thing%20to%20me%20%E2%80%94%20it%20changes%20the%20way%20you%20think%20about%20your%20money.%20You're%20not%20concerned%20about%20what%20happens%20to%20your%20living%20situation%20if%20you%20don't%20work%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20I%20could%20basically%20live%20this%20lifestyle%20forever%20for%20%2420%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20which%20to%20me%20is%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20looking%20for%20a%20new%20job%20right%20now.%20But%20because%20my%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20so%20cheap%2C%20%241%2C000%20a%20month%20is%20basically%20all%20I%20need%20to%20be%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI'm%20in%20a%20rural%20part%20of%20Japan%2C%20but%20still%20have%20access%20to%20the%20conveniences%20of%20a%20large%20city%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20in%20a%20place%20that%20is%20semi-rural%2C%20and%20my%20town%20is%20very%20small%20by%20size%20and%20population.%20But%20I%20live%20right%20on%20the%20border%20of%20Narita%2C%20so%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20leave%20this%20valley%2C%20it's%20all%20built%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20crazy%20convenient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rural%20neighborhood%20in%20Japan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cfab6ff533b039a884bd0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221407%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20in%20Watson's%20neighborhood.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ned%20Watson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20take%20a%20train%20from%20here%20to%20Tokyo.%20It's%20always%20on%20time%2C%20so%20I%20can%20plan%20when%20to%20leave%20my%20house%20and%20never%20wait%20more%20than%20a%20minute%20or%20two%20for%20the%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20come%20to%20the%20airport%20and%20then%20get%20on%20a%20train%20and%20in%2015%20minutes%2C%20I'm%20at%20my%20station%2C%20and%20then%20it's%20like%20a%2010-minute%20walk%20home.%20Being%20able%20to%20access%20a%20major%20international%20airport%20in%20that%20amount%20of%20time%20is%20really%20nice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20access%20to%20a%20very%20nice%20grocery%20store%20and%20an%20area%20that%20is%20modern%20and%20a%20place%20where%20wealthy%20Japanese%20people%20are%20happy%20to%20live.%20But%20my%20town%20is%20zoned%20for%20farming%2C%20so%20you%20can't%20just%20build%20houses%20here.%20That's%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20makes%20where%20I%20live%20a%20bit%20more%20interesting%20compared%20to%20some%20of%20the%20other%20places%20where%20people%20are%20finding%20cheaper%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20the%20akiya%20that%20are%20really%20cheap%20are%20in%20places%20that%20Japanese%20people%20have%20decided%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMake%20sure%20to%20research%20the%20neighborhood%20before%20buying%20an%20akiya%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20be%20aware%20of%20what%20drives%20the%20economy%20of%20that%20area.%20If%20it's%20a%20bunch%20of%20old%20people%20that%20are%20on%20fixed%20incomes%20because%20they're%20retired%2C%20then%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20development%20is%20going%20to%20happen.%20If%20you%20are%20expecting%20the%20place%20to%20become%20more%20exciting%20just%20because%20you%20showed%20up%20as%20a%20foreigner%2C%20that's%20not%20going%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20what%20specific%20things%20do%20you%20need%20to%20be%20happy%3F%20Do%20you%20like%20going%20out%20to%20eat%20at%20restaurants%3F%20Well%2C%20if%20you're%20at%20a%20place%20where%20they%20don't%20have%20many%20restaurants%2C%20that's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20fun.%20So%20really%20think%20about%20the%20area%20that%20the%20place%20is%20in%2C%20what%20type%20of%20personal%20infrastructure%20you're%20going%20to%20need%20to%20live%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20may%20be%20some%20communities%20where%20they're%20apprehensive%20about%20foreigners%20buying%20property%20because%20it's%20been%20in%20their%20family%20names%20forever.%20But%20if%20Japanese%20people%20aren't%20buying%20it%2C%20who%20else%20is%20going%20to%20buy%20it%3F%20It%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20foreigner%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20long%20you%20live%20here%2C%20there%20are%20going%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20experiences%20where%2C%20even%20if%20you're%20fluent%20in%20Japanese%20and%20you've%20been%20here%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20you're%20always%20going%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20foreigner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20my%20little%20community%2C%20I'm%20not%20seen%20specifically%20as%20a%20foreigner.%20I'm%20seen%20as%20that%20guy%20who%20lives%20over%20there%2C%20Ned%20%E2%80%94%20he's%20a%20foreigner.%20That%20can%20be%20complicated%20for%20people%20because%20in%20America%20you%20do%20your%20time%2C%20you%20learn%20the%20language%2C%20you%20make%20friends%2C%20you'll%20become%20an%20American.%20But%20in%20Japan%2C%20that%20doesn't%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-buys-cheap-abandoned-home-japan-peaceful-lower-cost-living-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708345141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cfe424f533b039a884eef2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-buys-cheap-abandoned-home-japan-peaceful-lower-cost-living-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ned%20Watson%20bought%20an%20abandoned%20Japanese%20home%2C%20known%20as%20an%20akiya%2C%20in%202019.%20It's%20brought%20him%20tranquility%20and%20a%20life%20free%20of%20financial%20burden.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy)%22%2C%22engagement