ten%20despite%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20that%20their%20complaints%20are%20politically%20motivated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20What%20began%20as%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20raid%20on%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20local%20strongman%E2%80%99s%20house%20has%20morphed%20into%20a%20wider%20movement%20against%20alleged%20land%20grabbing%2C%20systematic%20sexual%20assault%2C%20and%20the%20misuse%20of%20power%20by%20the%20ruling%20TMC%20in%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20approach%2C%20the%20issue%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20balloon%20into%20a%20major%20political%20crisis%20for%20the%20ruling%20party.%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20attacked%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20her%20party%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20creating%20a%20climate%20of%20fear%20and%20oppression.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20key%20arrest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESensing%20the%20public%20mood%2C%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20%E2%80%93%20already%20under%20pressure%20form%20the%20opposition%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20%E2%80%93%20took%20a%20series%20of%20steps%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20including%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20key%20accused%20Shiba%20Prasad%20Hazra%2C%20alias%20Shibu.%20Hazra%2C%20a%20Trinamool%20Congress%20block%20president%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20North%2024%20Parganas%20Zilla%20Parishad%2C%20was%20named%20by%20multiple%20women%20in%20serious%20sexual%20harassment%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHazra%20had%20notably%20been%20traced%20by%20reporters%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20prior%20to%20his%20arrest.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrCGMI_2qMFA%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20had%20also%20granted%20interviews%20proclaiming%20his%20innocence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20After%20first%20alleging%20that%20none%20of%20the%20complainants%20had%20mentioned%20%E2%80%98rape%E2%80%99%2C%20police%20have%20now%20added%20%E2%80%98gang%20rape%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98attempt%20to%20murder%E2%80%99%20charges%20against%20another%20local%20leader%2C%20Uttam%20Sardar%2C%20after%20a%20woman%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20and%20gave%20her%20statement%20before%20a%20magistrate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%2C%20two%20senior%20police%20officers%2C%20Deputy%20Inspector%20General%20(DIG)%20in%20charge%20of%20Barasat%20range%2C%20Sumit%20Kumar%20and%20Additional%20Director%20General%20(South%20Bengal)%20Siddinath%20Gupta%20were%20transferred.%20The%20transfers%20are%20deemed%20significant%2C%20with%20speculation%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20anticipated%20visit%20prompted%20the%20state%20administration%20to%20act%20proactively%2C%20particularly%20in%20light%20of%20attention%20on%20Sandeshkhali.%20As%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20noted%20in%20its%20ground%20report%2C%20many%20of%20the%20local%20women%20in%20the%20area%20had%20alleged%20that%20police%20were%20in%20cahoots%20with%20local%20TMC%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsandeshkhali-bengal-tmc-sexual-assault-rape-police%5C%22%3ESystemic%20Sexual%20Assault%2C%20an%20Oppressive%20TMC%20and%20Not%20Much%20Recourse%3A%20What%20Sandeshkhali%20Villagers%20Say%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThrough%20this%20all%2C%20the%20main%20accused%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20remains%20absconding.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(NCSC)%20chairman%2C%20Arun%20Halder%2C%20has%20recommended%20the%20imposition%20of%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20Halder%20has%20submitted%20a%20report%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20following%20his%20team%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20Sandeshkhali.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMamata%20Banerjee%20and%20%E2%80%98outsiders%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2015%2C%20when%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20finally%20addressed%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20unrest%2C%20she%20had%20attributed%20it%20to%20external%20interference.%20Many%20of%20her%20critics%20had%20noted%20that%20she%20was%20practically%20giving%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20and%20his%20two%20aides%20Uttam%20Sardar%20and%20Sibu%20Hazra.%20Dismissing%20the%20protests%20as%20opposition-driven%2C%20CM%20Banerjee%20accused%20BJP%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20of%20fomenting%20trouble%20in%20the%20area.%20Till%20February%2017%2C%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20ruling%20party%20had%20largely%20been%20in%20denial%20mode%20and%20maintained%20that%20the%20sexual%20assault%20and%20rape%20allegations%20were%20unsubstantiated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20targeted%20Shahjahan%20and%20entered%20the%20area%E2%80%A6and%20then%20outsiders%20entered%20through%20that%20same%20route.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20disturbances%20between%20the%20minorities%20and%20tribal%20people.%20I%20want%20to%20say%20that%20there%20is%20an%20RSS%20base%20and%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20disturbances.%20A%20riot%20occurred%20in%20the%20area%20seven-eight%20years%20ago.%20It%20is%20a%20spot%20vulnerable%20to%20tension%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Banerjee%20during%20her%20address%20in%20the%20assembly%20during%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20state%20budget.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20were%20the%20ones%20speaking%20with%20their%20faces%20covered%3F%20Who%20are%20they%3F%20Outsiders%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%