l%20factors%20like%20skin%20colour%20and%20body%20structure%3F%E2%80%9D%20political%20analyst%20Subhamoy%20Mitra%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20social%20media%2C%20West%20Bengal%20police%20has%20been%20issuing%20stern%20warnings%20to%20media%20outlets%20regarding%20the%20dissemination%20of%20information%20on%20the%20protests.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWilful%20misinformation%20is%20being%20spread%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20media%20that%20police%20custody%20was%20not%20sought%20for%20the%20two%20arrestees%20sent%20forward%20to%20the%20Ld%20Court%20today%20in%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20incident.%20This%20is%20absolutely%20false%20and%20misleading%E2%80%A6%E2%80%A6(1%2F3)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20West%20Bengal%20Police%20(%40WBPolice)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWBPolice%2Fstatus%2F1757101320857911432%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20women%20and%20child%20development%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20and%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%98IT%20cell%E2%80%99%20chief%20Amit%20Malviya%20have%20meanwhile%20been%20attempting%20to%20assert%20that%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20Scheduled%20Tribe%E2%80%9D%20women%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20are%20facing%20oppression%20from%20Rohingya%20refugees%20allegedly%20permitted%20to%20stay%20there%20by%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EContrary%20to%20their%20claims%2C%20investigations%20by%20the%20State%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Commission%20and%20a%20special%20team%20of%20the%20State%20Police%20have%20found%20no%20communal%20connections%20to%20the%20incident.%20This%20is%20corroborated%20by%20locals%20and%20analysts%20who%20emphasise%20that%20the%20participation%20of%20TMC%20leaders%20from%20various%20faiths%20in%20the%20alleged%20atrocities%20suggests%20that%20the%20issue%20is%20more%20political%20than%20communal%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20allegations%20brought%20forward%20by%20Sandeshkhali%E2%80%99s%20agitating%20women%20are%20very%20serious.%20They%20deserve%20proper%20investigation%20and%20demand%20administrative%20action.%20While%20acknowledging%20their%20grievances%20with%20utmost%20respect%2C%20it%20is%20concerning%20to%20observe%20that%20a%20section%20of%20the%20media%20is%20collaborating%20with%20a%20political%20party%20to%20portray%20the%20entire%20incident%20in%20a%20communal%20colour%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20context%20of%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20society%20and%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20political%20analyst%20Udayan%20Banerjee.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFailure%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20with%20necessary%20seriousness%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20dangerous%20escalation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20all-women%20police%20team%2C%20formed%20to%20investigate%20abuse%20allegations%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20has%20identified%20potential%20cases%20of%20forced%20labour%20and%20molestation%20during%20interviews%20with%20over%2070%20women%20across%20several%20villages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2016%2C%20a%20BJP%20%E2%80%98fact-finding%20team%E2%80%99%20appointed%20by%20BJP%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%2C%20on%20its%20way%20to%20the%20area%2C%20was%20stopped%20by%20the%20police%20halfway.%20Police%20cited%20the%20fact%20that%20Section%20144%20had%20been%20imposed%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%20In%20protest%2C%20the%20BJP%20team%20staged%20a%20sit-in%20and%20met%20West%20Bengal%20Governor%20C.V.%20Ananda%20Bose.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fsandeshkhali-violence-sup