2840%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20houses%20of%20people%20allegedly%20displaced%20by%20TMC%20leaders%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolice%20also%20stopped%20West%20Bengal%20Pradesh%20Congress%20chief%20Adhir%20Chowdhury%20from%20visiting%20Sandeshkhali.%20Chowdhury%20is%20a%20known%20critic%20of%20CM%20Banerjee%20and%20accused%20her%20of%20communalising%20the%20issue%20to%20divert%20attention.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBengal%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%20is%20playing%20with%20fire.%20She%20is%20claiming%20this%20to%20be%20a%20clash%20between%20tribal%20and%20Muslim%20communities.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20communal%20issue%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20issue%20of%20those%20in%20power%20exploiting%20the%20vulnerable.%20The%20attempt%20to%20communalise%20this%20is%20a%20ploy%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20her%20party%E2%80%99s%20misdeeds%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Chowdhury.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20government%20has%20reinforced%20Section%20144%20in%20a%20500-meter%20radius%20around%20seven-gram%20panchayats%20and%20nine%20islands%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20with%20significant%20police%20presence.%20Although%20originally%20lifted%20by%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%2C%20the%20Section%20144%20imposition%20is%20now%20extended%20until%20February%2019.%20A%20%E2%80%9Cconfidence-building%E2%80%9D%20public%20rally%20scheduled%20by%20Trinamool%20Congress%20was%20also%20cancelled%20at%20the%20last%20minute.%20Instead%2C%20senior%20leaders%20and%20ministers%20Partha%20Bhowmik%20and%20Sujit%20Bose%20said%20they%20would%20visit%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20interact%20with%20locals%20in%20a%20closed-door%20venue.%20The%20ruling%20party%20has%20announced%20a%20larger%20rally%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20on%20March%205.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Medieval%20barbarism%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20so%20far%20arrested%2017%20people%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20unrest%20including%20key%20accused%20local%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Uttam%20Hazra%2C%20CPI(M)%20state%20committee%20member%20and%20former%20MLA%20of%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20Nirapada%20Sardar%2C%20and%20local%20BJP%20leader%20Bikash%20Singh%20along%20with%20some%20locals.%20While%20Uttam%20was%20arrested%20based%20on%20complaints%20of%20torture%20and%20atrocities%20by%20villagers%2C%20opposition%20leaders%20were%20arrested%20based%20on%20key%20accused%20Shibu%20Hazra%E2%80%99s%20complaints.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSandeshkhali%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20state%20of%20affairs%20in%20West%20Bengal.%C2%A0%20It%20can%20only%20be%20compared%20with%20medieval%20barbarism.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20government%20of%20miscreants%20where%20victims%20of%20exploitation%20and%20abuse%20are%20hiding%20in%20fear%20and%20criminals%20are%20being%20protected%20by%20the%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20stated%20CPI(M)%20central%20committee%20member%20Sujan%20Chakraborty.%20Chakraborty%20led%20a%20rally%20in%20front%20of%20the%20district%20police%20chief%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20in%20Basirhat%2C%20on%20February%2015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20petition%20has%20been%20filed%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20urging%20for%20a%20dedicated%20investigation%20into%20the%20incidents%20of%20violence%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20either%20by%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20or%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20protests%20over%20land%20disputes%2C%20and%20accusations%20of%20violence%20engulf%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20the%20repercussions%20extend%20far%20beyond%20the%20village%2C%20casting%20a%20long%20shadow%20on%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20political%20landscape.%20The%20ruling%20TMC%2C%20already%20under%20pressure%20over%20multiple%20corruption%20charges%20against%20its%20top%20leadership%2C%20finds%20itself%20under%20intense%20scrutiny%2C%20with%20simmering%20discontent%20potentially%20influencing%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20A%20major%20concern%20for%20the%20party%20is%20the%20massive%20participation%20of%20women%20in%20the%20protest%20against%20the%20alleged%20%E2%80%98reign%20of%20terror%E2%80%99%20by%20Trinamool%20congress%20strongmen%20in%20the%20region.%20Women%20constitute%20a%20crucial%20voting%20bloc%20for%20the%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20announcement%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20is%20still%20pending.%20The%20extent%20to%20which%20this%20incident%20will%20influence%20the%20vote%20hinges%20on%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20sustained%20protest%20duration.%20While%20the%20issue%20of%20women%20is%20sensitive%2C%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20vote%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20relatively%20modest%2C%E2%80%9D%20stated%20political%20analyst%20Biswanath%20Chakraborty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708342225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112624%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.25.27-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fsandeshkhali-unrest-as-women-led-protests-escalate-tmcs-outsider-claims-find-little-resonance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TMC%20leaders%20including%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20women%20who%20complained%20of%20systemic%20sexual%20harassment%20are%20propelled%20by%20politics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fsandeshkhali-unrest-as-women-led-protests-escalate-tmcs-outsider-claims-find-little-resonance%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20'MSP%20Subsidy%20for%20Consumers%20Not%20Farmers%2C%20They%20Will%20Diversify%20Crops%20If%20Govt%20Amps%20Up%20Support'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F19161738%2FKT-19-Feb.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20hard-hitting%20interview%20where%20he%20frequently%20counters%20and%20rebuts%20many%20of%20the%20points%20made%20earlier%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20agriculture%20economist%20Ashok%20Gulati%2C%20professor%20of%20Economics%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20Himanshu%2C%20has%20emphatically%20said%20that%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20is%20%E2%80%9Ca%20subsidy%20to%20consumers%20and%20not%20to%20farmers%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Himanshu%20has%20also%20argued%20that%20when%20farmers%20ask%20for%20MSP%20to%20be%20made%20legally%20binding%20what%20they%20are%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20saying%20is%20that%20the%20government%20must%20fulfil%20its%20five-decade%20commitment%20to%20properly%20implement%20and%20enforce%20the%20MSP%20regime%20it%20has%20claimed%20to%20be%20committed%20to.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20says%2C%20MSP%20has%20applied%20to%20wheat%20and%20rice%20but%20rarely%2C%20infrequently%20and%20usually%20not%20properly%20to%20all%20the%20remaining%2021%20crops%20to%20which%20it%E2%80%99s%20supposed%20to%20apply.%20Legal-binding%20will%20ensure%20it%20does.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FVGpVNFejsYQ%3Fsi%3DXAkAWvYn_lBW1L0X%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanshu%20said%20that%20if%20MSP%20is%20properly%20applied%20to%20the%2021%20crops%2C%20other%20than%20wheat%20and%20rice%2C%20it%20will%20provide%20an%20incentive%20for%20farmers%20to%20diversify.%20As%20he%20said%2C%20treat%20farmers%20like%20businessmen.%20They%20will%20respond%20in%20their%20own%20interest%20to%20the%20incentives%20offered%20to%20them%20if%2C%20repeat%20if%2C%20the%20MSP%20regime%20is%20applied%20to%20all%20the%20other%20crops%20to%20which%20its%20meant%20to.%20Taking%20the%20example%20of%20edible%20oil%20which%2C%20at%20present%2C%20is%20imported%20at%20great%20expense%2C%20if%20MSP%20is%20applied%20properly%20to%20oil%20seeds%20(or%20pulses)%20the%20need%20for%20import%20will%20immediately%20diminish%20if%20not%20disappear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20other%20important%20point%20discussed%20with%20Himanshu%20are%20newspaper%20reports%20that%20the%20government%20is%20considering%20giving%20a%20five-year%20MSP%20commitment%20for%20pulses%2C%20maize%20and%20cotton.%20Himanshu%20says%20he%20cannot%20understand%20why%20it%E2%80%99s%20limited%20to%20five%20years%20and%20questions%20whether%20its%20legally%20binding%20or%20will%20be%20like%20the%20present%20MSP.%20He%20also%20asks%20why%20it%20is%20not%20extended%20to%20all%20the%20other%2023%20crops%20to%20which%20MSP%20is%20supposed%20to%20apply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20questions%20he%20was%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20Why%20do%20you%20believe%20making%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20for%2023%20crops%20legally%20binding%20is%20the%20right%20way%20of%20helping%20farmers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20How%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20Ashok%20Gulati%2C%20who%20has%20told%20me%20that%20making%20MSP%20legally%20binding%20would%20be%20anti-farmer%3F%20He%20says%20when%20the%20MSP%20is%20higher%20than%20the%20market%20price%2C%20private%20traders%20will%20refuse%20to%20buy%20thus%20either%20leaving%20farmers%20with%20unsold%20surplus%20or%20forcing%20the%20government%20to%20step-in%20and%20buy%20everything.%20The%20first%20would%20be%20a%20disaster%20for%20farmers.%20The%20second%20would%20have%20very%20adverse%20budgetary%20and%20fiscal%20implications%20for%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20According%20to%20a%20study%20done%20in%202018-19%20by%20Ashok%20Gulati%20and%20quoted%20by%20the%20Business%20Standard%20only%208.8%25%20of%20agricultural%20households%20sell%20any%20crop%20under%20MSP.%20Gulati%20says%20that%20figure%20is%20perhaps%2010%25%20today.%20So%20clearly%20MSP%20is%20not%20a%20concern%20for%2090%25%20of%20agricultural%20households.%20Why%20then%20should%20it%20be%20made%20legally%20binding%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4)%20Let%20me%20raise%20a%20second%20issue.%20Gulati%20says%20high-flying%20sectors%20of%20Indian%20agriculture%20like%20poultry%2C%20growing%20at%208-9%25%2C%20fisheries%2C%20growing%20at%207-8%25%2C%20and%20milk%2C%20growing%20at%205-6%25%2C%20do%20not%20have%20access%20to%20any%20MSP%20regime%20and%20yet%20are%20flourishing.%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20this%20mean%20that%20a%20legally%20binding%20MSP%20is%20not%20necessary%20for%20agricultural%20growth%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5)%20Do%20you%20have%20an%20estimate%20for%20what%20a%20legally%20binding%20MSP%20for%2023%20crops%20would%20cost%3F%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20puts%20it%20at%2010%20lakh%20crore.%20But%20won%E2%80%99t%20it%20vary%20crop%20by%20crop%20and%20region%20by%20region%20and%20depend%20on%20what%20the%20market%20price%20is%20and%20how%20much%20the%20government%20has%20to%20make-up%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6)%20The%20second%20connected%20question%20is%20how%20should%20MSP%20be%20calculated.%20Farmers%20are%20insisting%20that%20it%20should%20be%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20C2%20%2B%2050%25.%20On%20this%20specific%20issue%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20your%20position%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7)%20Ashok%20Gulati%20says%20that%20if%20MSP%20is%20calculated%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20C2%20%2B%2050%25%20food%20prices%20would%20increase%20by%2025-30%25%20which%20will%20have%20a%20huge%20impact%20on%20inflation%20right%20across%20the%20economy.%20How%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8)%20At%20the%20moment%20and%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years%20the%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20giving%20free%20wheat%20and%20rice%20to%20over%20800%20million%20people.%20If%20MSP%20is%20fixed%20at%20C2%20%2B%2050%25%20this%20would%20hugely%20increase%20the%20cost%20for%20government%20which%20would%20either%20kick-up%20the%20fiscal%20deficit%20or%20substantially%20reduce%20resources%20for%20other%20essential%20expenditure%20such%20as%20health%2C%20education%20and%20even%20agricultural%20development%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9)%20Let%20me%20put%20a%20wider%20thought%20to%20you.%20Rather%20than%20help%20farmers%20through%20a%20legally%20binding%20MSP%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20view%20they%20should%20be%20given%20income%20support%2C%20which%20I%20believe%20is%20the%20practice%20in%20China%2C%20another%20country%20where%20agriculture%20happens%20mainly%20on%20small%20holdings.%20This%20would%20leave%20farmers%20free%20to%20decide%20whether%20they%20want%20seed%2C%20power%2C%20fertilisers%20and%20use%20the%20income%20support%20as%20they%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10)%20Let%20me%20put%20a%20second%20thought%20to%20you.%20The%20real%20concern%20is%20to%20find%20effective%20ways%20of%20increasing%20real%20incomes%20for%20farmers.%20How%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20the%20view%20that%20rather%20than%20grow%20rice%20in%20Punjab%2C%20which%20is%20an%20environmentally%20unwise%20choice%2C%20we%20need%20to%20incentivize%20them%20to%20move%20to%20high-value%20agriculture%20such%20as%20fruit%2C%20vegetables%2C%20livestock%20and%20fisheries%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E11)%20It%E2%80%99s%20often%20said%20the%20core%20problem%20is%20that%20governments%20in%20India%20have%20a%20pro-consumer%20bias.%20They%20care%20more%20about%20controlling%20inflation%20for%20urban%20populations%20than%20helping%20farmers%20increase%20their%20income.%20Do%20you%20agree%20that%20lies%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20problem%20farmers%20face%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E12)%20In%20a%20piece%20you%20wrote%20for%20the%20Indian%20Express%20on%20February%2017%20you%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20unfair%20to%20treat%20the%20cost%20of%20procuring%20rice%20and%20wheat%20as%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20MSP%20programme%20for%20rice%20and%20wheat.%20In%20fact%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20it%20is%20a%20subsidy%20to%20consumers%20and%20not%20to%20farmers.%E2%80%9D%20Can%20you%20explain%20how%20MSP%20for%20rice%20and%20wheat%20is%20a%20subsidy%20for%20consumers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708342185000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F19161738%2FKT-19-Feb.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fhimanshu-karan-thapar-msp-ashok-gulati-farmers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Economist%20Himanshu%20says%20that%20if%20MSP%20is%20properly%20applied%20to%20the%2021%20crops%2C%20other%20than%20wheat%20and%20rice%2C%20it%20will%20provide%20an%20incentive%20for%20farmers%20to%20diversify.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fhimanshu-karan-thapar-msp-ashok-gulati-farmers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Crew%20abandon%20ship%20off%20Yemen%20as%20Houthis%20claim%20attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708342140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FFEEA%2Fproduction%2F_132685256_0dab03d5fdba2f2ccbda1de9be29c48be565852a.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68337027%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Yemeni%20group%20says%20its%20missiles%20damaged%20a%20British-registered%20cargo%20ship%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A66%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68337027%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-