without-punishment-in-a-viral-dog-assault-case%2Farticleshow%2F107823368.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Remark%20After%20Chandigarh%20Mayor%20Quits%2C%20Councillors%20Switch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20today%20said%20that%20the%20resignation%20of%20BJP%20leader%20Manoj%20Sonkar%20proved%20that%20the%20elections%20were%20manipulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mayor's%20resignation%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20there%20was%20manipulation%20in%20the%20election.%20If%20the%20election%20is%20not%20won%2C%20our%20councilors%20are%20being%20purchased%20and%20broken%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20come%20a%20day%20after%20Mr%20Sonkar%20resigned%20from%20the%20post%20ahead%20of%20Supreme%20Court%20hearing%20a%20petition%20claiming%20alleged%20tampering%20in%20the%20mayoral%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sonkar%20had%20secured%20victory%20in%20the%20closely%20watched%20election%20held%20on%20January%2030%2C%20defeating%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20Kuldeep%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20witnessed%20Mr%20Sonkar%20obtaining%2016%20votes%20against%20the%20AAP%20candidate's%2012.%20The%20BJP's%20victory%20faced%20controversy%20with%208%20votes%20being%20declared%20invalid%2C%20leading%20to%20intense%20scrutiny%20and%20accusations%20from%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20strict%20view%20of%20the%20alleged%20defacement%20of%20ballot%20papers%20during%20the%20Chandigarh%20mayoral%20election%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20that%20the%20returning%20officer%2C%20Anil%20Masih%2C%20should%20be%20prosecuted.%20The%20court%20said%20this%20after%20seeking%20answers%20from%20Mr%20Masih%2C%20marking%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20independent%20India%20that%20a%20returning%20officer%20has%20been%20cross-examined%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20elections%2C%20three%20of%20AAP's%20councillors%20-%20Poonam%20Devi%2C%20Neha%2C%20and%20Gurcharan%20Kala%20-%20defected%20to%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20development%2C%20the%20BJP's%20strength%20in%20the%2035-member%20Chandigarh%20Municipal%20Corporation%20increased%20to%2017.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20BJP%20enjoys%20the%20support%20of%20one%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20councillor%2C%20and%20BJP's%20Chandigarh%20MP%20Kirron%20Kher%20has%20voting%20rights%20as%20an%20ex-officio%20member%2C%20bringing%20their%20total%20to%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%2C%20now%20left%20with%2010%20councillors%2C%20and%20its%20ally%20Congress%20with%20seven%2C%20find%20themselves%20in%20a%20challenging%20situation.%20The%20election%20aftermath%20has%20been%20marked%20by%20chaos%2C%20with%20allegations%20of%20cheating%20and%20electoral%20irregularities.%20The%20opposition%2C%20including%20the%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20councillors%2C%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20not%20adhering%20to%20due%20electoral%20processes%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20presiding%20officer%2C%20Anil%20Masih%2C%20was%20caught%20%26quot%3Btampering%26quot%3B%20with%20ballot%20papers%20in%20a%20video%20submitted%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20has%20vehemently%20denied%20these%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708340580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ffqpflim_arvind-kejriwal-ani_625x300_19_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-chandigarh-mayor-resigns-amid-rigging-probe-arvind-kejriwal-quip-5086373%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal%20today%20said%20that%20the%20resignation%20of%20BJP%20leader%20Manoj%20Sonkar%20proved%20that%20the%20elections%20were%20manipulated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-chandigarh-mayor-resigns-amid-rigging-probe-arvind-kejriwal-quip-5086373%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-chandigarh-mayor-resigns-amid-rigging-probe-arvind-kejriwal-quip-5086373%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-chandigarh-mayor-resigns-amid-rigging-probe-arvind-kejriwal-quip-5086373%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Stays%20LS%20Privilege%20Committee%20Proceedings%20Against%20Bengal%20Officials%20Over%20BJP%20MP's%20Complaint%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25132016%2FSupreme-court4.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20stayed%20the%20proceedings%20of%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20privilege%20committee%20against%20Bengal%20bureaucrats%20and%20top%20cops%2C%20over%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Sukanta%20Majumdar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajumdar%20has%20alleged%20that%20he%20had%20been%20mistreated%20by%20the%20Bengal%20police%20as%20he%20was%20making%20his%20way%20towards%20Sandeshkhali%20in%20the%20state%20on%20February%2013%20and%2014.%20Sandeshkhali%20has%20been%20on%20the%20boil%20since%20hundreds%20of%20women%20alleged%20that%20they%20had%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20local%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20writ%20petition%20challenging%20the%20proceedings%20had%20been%20filed%20by%20Bengal%20chief%20secretary%20Bhagwati%20Prasad%20Gopalika%2C%20the%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%20magistrate%20Sharad%20Kumar%20Dwivedi%2C%20the%20Bengal%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20Rajeev%20Kumar%2C%20the%20Basirhat%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Dr.%20Hossain%20Mehedi%20Rehman%2C%20and%20the%20Basirhat%20Additional%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Partha%20Ghosh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20passed%20the%20interim%20order%20while%20issuing%20notice%20to%20the%20above%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-stays-lok-sabha-privileges-committee-proceedings-against-west-bengal-officials-on-bjp-mps-complaint-249821%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20had%20been%20asked%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Privileges%20Committee%20at%2010.30%20am%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Bengal%20government%2C%20Senior%20Advocates%20Kapil%20Sibal%20and%20Dr%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20said%20Majumdar%20and%20his%20supporters%20had%20violated%20Section%20144%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Procedure%20Code%20in%20attempting%20to%20land%20Sandeshkhali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajumdar%20had%20complaint%20that%20police%20had%20deliberately%20and%20%E2%80%9Cbrutally%E2%80%9D%20injured%20him%20with%20their%20conduct%20as%20he%20tried%20to%20make%20his%20way%20to%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20argued%20that%20a%20parliamentarian%E2%80%99s%20privilege%20should%20not%20be%20available%20when%20they%20are%20not%20performing%20parliamentary%20duties%2C%20and%20instead%20engaging%20in%20political%20activity.%20The%20police%20officers%20and%20bureaucrats%20were%20not%20in%20the%20area%20at%20that%20time%20either%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrivileges%20are%20meant%20to%20protect%20your%20work%20as%20a%20Parliamentarian.%20Otherwise%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20breach%20of%20privileges%20in%20every%20case%2C%20nobody%20can%20be%20arrested%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singhvi%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI-led%20bench%20set%20a%20deadline%20of%20four%20weeks%20on%20the%20notice%20and%20stayed%20further%20proceedings%20in%20pursuance%20of%20the%20notice%20issued%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretariat%20against%20the%20state%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708340456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%