e...%26quot%3B%20-%20came%20as%20a%20surprise%20give%20the%20three-time%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20a%20supporter%20and%20attended%20all%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20though%2C%20he%20his%20concern%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20consensus%20within%20the%20bloc%20on%20seat-sharing%20deals%2C%20worries%20also%20flagged%20earlier%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20and%20others%2C%20including%20Mr%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20to%20save%20the%20country%2C%20we%20have%20to%20forget%20(our)%20differences...%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20jumped%20at%20the%20chance%20to%20criticise%20its%20rivals%2C%20with%20party%20spokesperson%20RS%20Pathania%20telling%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20ragtag%20conglomerate%20in%20which%20participants%20have%20least%20convergence%20on%20any%20issues%20of%20policy%2C%20agenda%20or%20manifesto.%20The%20alliance%20almost%20falls%20(apart)%20like%20a%20house%20of%20cards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PDP's%20move%20comes%20days%20after%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20declared%20his%20party%2C%20while%20remaining%20part%20of%20the%20under-pressure%20INDIA%20grouping%2C%20%26quot%3Bwill%20contest%20elections%20on%20its%20own%20strength%26quot%3B.%20Sources%20said%20this%20call%20was%20based%20on%20an%20internal%20assessment%20that%20said%20the%20party%20could%20win%20at%20least%20three%20seats%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20the%20National%20Conference%20is%20unwilling%20to%20give%20up%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708336200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https