20such%20as%20schools%2C%20toilets%2C%20buses%20and%20trains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movie%20shows%20how%20the%20strict%20maintenance%20of%20endogamy%20comes%20to%20play%20at%20any%20cost%20in%20all%20three%20forms%20of%20discrimination%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Holocaust%2C%20in%20the%20Jim%20Crow%20era%20and%20in%20India%20%E2%80%94%20such%20examples%2C%20the%20narration%20and%20the%20powerful%20scenery%20makes%20her%20hypothesis%20convincing.%20Some%20members%20of%20the%20audience%20were%20also%20seen%20clapping%20at%20the%20powerful%20ending%20of%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20concentrates%20on%20the%20past%20and%20the%20present%20life%20of%20Wilkerson%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20sound%20like%20a%20documentary%20nor%20a%20biography%20of%20the%20author.%20The%20director%20keeps%20the%20audience%E2%80%99s%20attention%20glued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Ambedkar%20angle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20film%2C%20Wilkerson%20meets%20Indian%20scholar%20Dr%20Suraj%20Yengde%20from%20Harvard%20during%20her%20visit%20to%20the%20country.%20He%20gives%20her%20additional%20insights%20on%20the%20caste%20system.%20Yengde%20asserts%20that%20Ambedkar%20is%20close%20to%20the%20African%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EOrigin%3C%2Fi%3E%20underlines%20how%20caste%20is%20an%20intrinsic%20factor%20in%20a%20developing%20country%20like%20India%20where%20there%20still%20continues%20an%20inhuman%20practice%20of%20manual%20scavenging%3A%20Dalits%20enter%20into%20a%20manhole%20full%20of%20human%20excreta%20without%20any%20protection%20and%20only%20the%20oil%20on%20their%20body%2C%20clearly%2C%20technological%20advances%20remain%20%E2%80%9Cuntouchable%E2%80%9D%20in%20this%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20uses%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20original%20voice%20and%20his%20opinion%20on%20endogamy%20as%20a%20preserver%20of%20caste%20very%20succinctly%20to%20make%20a%20point.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20were%20expecting%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20character%20as%20one%20of%20the%20main%20ones%2C%20you%20are%20in%20for%20a%20slight%20disappointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathania%20looks%20perfect%20as%20Ambedkar%20perhaps%20more%20compelling%20than%20Jabbar%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20movie%20(2000)%20where%20Mammooty%20portrayed%20the%C2%A0%20same%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20shown%20in%20various%20avatars%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20student%20of%20Columbia%20university%20on%20the%20campus%2C%20in%20and%20around%20New%20York%20and%20also%20during%20the%20Mahad%20satyagraha%20%E2%80%94%20but%20his%20screen%20presence%20is%20limited%20and%20he%20has%20no%20dialogues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20director%20had%20shown%20a%20short%20scene%20of%20Ambedkar%20presenting%20his%20paper%20%E2%80%9CCastes%20In%20India%20%E2%80%93%20Their%20Mechanism%2C%20Genesis%20and%20Development%20(1919)%E2%80%9D%20talking%20about%20endogamy%2C%20in%20front%20of%20his%20professors%2C%20his%20character%20would%20have%20come%20really%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20silver%20lining%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbedkar%E2%80%99s%20foray%20on%20the%20big%20screen%20in%20Hollywood%20in%202024%20is%20sure%20to%20enthuse%20people%20across%20the%20world%20who%20believe%20in%20human%20rights.%20It%E2%80%99s%20interesting%20to%20note%20that%20Richard%20Attenborough%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EGandhi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(1982)%20did%20not%20even%20mention%20Ambedkar%20in%20a%20passing%20reference.%20It%20seemed%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%98outcasted%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2041%20years%20later%2C%20we%20finally%20have%20a%20Hollywood%20movie%20showing%20Ambedkar%20in%20a%20motion%20picture%20led%20by%20an%20African%20American%20lead%2C%20a%20powerful%20combination%20of%20the%20oppressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20the%20movie%20has%20received%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscreenrant.com%2Forigin-movie-rotten-tomatoes-ava-duvernay-movie-comparison%2F%5C%22%3Erave%3C%2Fa%3E%20reviews%20on%20%3Cem%3ERotten%20Tomatoes%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20has%20been%20appreciated%20for%20the%20incredible%20performance%20of%20the%20lead%20actor%20and%20unique%20storytelling%20by%20the%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOrigin%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20released%20in%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK.%20The%20India%20release%20dates%20are%20not%20yet%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708335421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F19145859%2F7963FDA9-9BB0-4947-94EB-67488D5513BB.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fb-r-ambedkar-makes-his-hollywood-debut-in-origin-which-explores-global-connections-of-caste%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20film%20is%20based%20on%20the%20book%20'Caste%3A%20The%20Origins%20of%20Our%20Discontents'%20and%20has%20garnered%20good%20reviews.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fb-r-ambedkar-makes-his-hollywood-debut-in-origin-which-explores-global-connections-of-caste%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jungkook%20wins%20at%202024%20People's%20Choice%20Awards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708335348000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107819613%2Cimgsize-63336.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbtss-jungkook-and-stray-kids-win-big-at-2024-peoples-choice-awards%2Farticleshow%2F107819488.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107819488.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBTS's%20Jungkook%20wins%20Male%20Artist%20of%20the%20Year%20at%20the%202024%20People's%20Choice%20Awards%2C%20showcasing%20his%20exceptional%20vocals.%20Stray%20Kids%20secures%20the%20Group%2FDuo%20of%20the%20Year%20award%2C%20continuing%20to%20capt