0signs%20of%20an%20accord%20on%20the%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20meeting%20late%20Sunday%20the%20government%20-%20facing%20a%20second%20round%20of%20farmers'%20protests%2C%20this%20time%20just%20weeks%20before%20a%20general%20election%20-%20relented%20on%20the%20subject%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fmsp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMSP%2C%20or%20minimum%20support%20price%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20proposing%20a%20five-year%20contract%20to%20buy%20pulses%2C%20maize%2C%20and%20cotton.%20The%20farmers%20-%20for%20whom%20MSP%20is%20a%20red-flag%20issue%20-%20asked%2C%20and%20were%20given%2C%2048%20hours%20to%20confer%2C%20and%20have%20put%20'Delhi%20Chalo%202.0'%20on%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20legal%20assurance%20for%20MSP%20is%20seen%20as%20No.1%20on%20the%20farmers'%20wish%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sides%20met%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20with%20the%20government%20represented%20by%20three%20union%20ministers%2C%20including%20Commerce%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20signs%2C%20though%2C%20are%20not%20encouraging%2C%20with%20farmer%20leaders%20telling%20NDTV%20the%20government%20must%20offer%20guarantees%20on%20all%2023%20crops%2C%20and%20not%20just%20dal%20or%20maize.%20Those%20from%20Punjab%20-%20from%20where%20a%20bulk%20of%20protesting%20farmers%20hail%20-%20have%20pointed%20out%20their%20share%20of%20growing%20of%20pulses%20or%20maize%20is%2C%20in%20any%20case%2C%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20benefit%20to%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%20farmers%20from%20this%20incomplete%20proposal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarmers-Government%20Agree%20On%20MSP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20brief%2C%20the%20following%20points%20emerged%20from%20the%20Chandigarh%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUnion%20cooperative%20societies%20like%20NCCF%2C%20or%20National%20Cooperative%20Consumers%20Federation%2C%20and%20NAFED%2C%20or%20National%20Agricultural%20Cooperative%20Marketing%20Federation%20of%20India%20-%20will%20sign%20a%20five-year%20contract%20to%20buy%20dal%20or%20maize%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUnder%20this%20contract%20the%20above%20crops%20will%20be%20bought%20at%20MSPs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20will%20be%20no%20limit%20on%20purchase%20quantities%C2%A0and%C2%A0a%C2%A0website%20will%20be%20made.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20said%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmer-leaders-meeting-piyush-goyal-proposal-msp-crops-underground-water-inform-tomorrow-5083673%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoffer%20is%20part%20of%20a%20long-term%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20increase%20maize%20production%20%26quot%3Bas%20a%20major%20feed%20stock%20for%20grain-based%20ethanol%20supply%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-5-year-proposal-to-farmers-demanding-safety-net-on-crop-prices-5084475%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_bigstory%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECentre's%205-Year%20Formula%20To%20Farmers%20For%20Crop%20Prices%20Safety%20Net%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20save%20Punjab's%20farming%20sector%2C%20improve%20groundwater%20table%2C%20and%20save%20land%20-%20already%20under%20stress%20-%20from%20getting%20barren%2C%20he%20explained.%C2%A0The%20government%20-%20trying%20to%20encourage%20maize%20and%20dal%20is%20part%20of%20its%20%26quot%3Bcrop%20diversification%26quot%3B%20-%20set%20the%20MSP%20maize%20at%20Rs%202%2C090%20per%20quintal%20last%20year%2C%20up%20from%20Rs%201%2C760%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20over%20groundwater%20have%20been%20expressed%20in%20the%20past%20too%3B%20in%20November%20last%20year%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20warned%20Punjab%20to%20take%20measures%20-%20including%20switching%20to%20maize.%20This%20was%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20hearing%20on%20air%20quality%20pollution%20-%20triggered%20by%20burning%20of%20farm%20(paddy)%20waste%20-%20in%20the%20Delhi%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpunjab-chief-minister-bhagwant-mann-said-we-had-asked-for-msp-guarantee-on-purchase-of-pulses-5083855%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWe%20Asked%20For%20MSP%20Guarantee%20For%20Purchase%20Of%20Pulses%26quot%3B%3A%20Bhagwant%20Mann%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20estimated%20record%20346.13%20lakh%20tons%20of%20maize%20was%20grown%20in%202022%2F23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurrent%20MSP%20Scheme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%20MSP%20is%20offered%20on%2023%20crops%20apart%20from%20staples%20like%20paddy%2C%20wheat%2C%20pulses%2C%20and%20maize.%20These%20include%20ragi%2C%20groundnut%2C%20soybean%2C%20sunflower%20seeds%2C%20barley%2C%20rapeseed%2C%20and%20mustard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2023%20prices%20were%20announced%20in%20June%2C%20when%20kharif%20crop%20MSPs%20were%20increased%20-%20and%20fixed%20at%20a%20level%20at%20least%201.5%20times%20the%20All-India%20weighted%20average%20cost%20of%20production%20-%C2%A0%26quot%3Bto%20ensure%20remunerative%20prices%20for%20their%20produce%20and%20to%20encourage%20crop%20diversification%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarmers'%20MSP%20Demand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20a%20legal%20backing%20for%20MSPs%2C%20the%20farmers%20want%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission's%20recommendations%20to%20be%20implemented%2C%20as%20well%20as%20pension%20for%20farmers%20and%20farm%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Swaminathan%20Commission's%20recommendations%20on%20MSP%20are%20worth%20mentioning%2C%20since%20it%20suggested%20the%20floor%20price%20be%20set%20at%20least%2050%20per%20cent%20above%20the%20weighted%20average%20cost%20of%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-set-for-mega-delhi-chalo-march-what-are-the-key-demands-5047380%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhat%20Are%20Key%20Demands%20Of%20Farmers%20That%20Remain%20Unresolved%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20known%20as%20the%20C2%2B50%20formula%2C%20which%20factors%20cost%20of%20capital%20and%20land%20rent%20in%20setting%20MSPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20umbrella%20farmer%20body%20behind%20this%20round%20of%20protests%2C%20the%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%2C%20has%20indicated%20it%20is%20unwilling%20to%20accept%20anything%20less%20than%20that%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20MSP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMSP%20is%20a%20form%20of%20market%20intervention%20and%20refers%20to%20a%20set%20fixed%20by%20the%20government%20to%20protect%20farmers%20from%20a%20steep%20fall%20in%20crop%20prices%3B%20for%20example%2C%20during%20a%20bumper%20crop%20when%20prices%20plummet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEssentially%2C%20every%20year%20the%20government%20purchases%20a%20quantity%20of%20certain%20crops%2C%20the%20list%20and%20prices%20of%20which%20are%20announced%20before%20sowing.%20The%20purpose%20is%20not%20only%20to%20allow%20farmers%20a%20minimum%20return%20on%20(part%20of)%20their%20investment%20but%20also%20procure%20crops%20for%20the%20government's%20public%20distribution%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MSP%20is%20the%20floor%20price%2C%20i.e.%2C%20it%20is%20the%20minimum%20at%20which%20a%20crop%20can%20be%20bought%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Archives%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarm-laws-scrapped-farm-laws-to-be-cancelled-says-pm-modi-what-are-the-three-black-laws-2617490%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFarm%20Laws%20To%20Be%20Scrapped.%20What%20Are%20Three%20%26quot%3BBlack%26quot%3B%20Laws%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMSPs%2C%20however%2C%20have%20no%20legal%20backing%2C%20meaning%20the%20government%20is%20not%20obliged%20to%20buy%2C%20for%20example%2C%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20a%20farmer's%20paddy%20crop%20at%20the%20floor%20price.%20And%20it%20is%20this%20that%20the%20farmers%20want%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20over%20MSP%20made%20headlines%20four%20years%20ago%20after%20the%20second%20of%20the%20Modi%20government's%20three%20%26quot%3Bblack%26quot%3B%20laws%2C%20which%20were%20scrapped%20after%20the%20farmers'%202020%2F21%20protest.%20This%20law%20-%20the%20Farmers%20(Empowerment%20and%20Protection)%20Agreement%20of%20Price%20Assurance%20and%20Farm%20Services%20Act%20-%20said%20crop%20prices%20would%20be%20determined%20by%20market%20forces%20-%20i.e.%2C%20farmers%20would%20get%20more%20for%20in-demand%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%2C%20however%2C%20felt%20this%20would%20abolish%2C%20by%20default%2C%20the%20MSP%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-says-misinformation-being-spread-that-farmers-wont-get-right-prices-amid-protests-over-farm-bills-2297418%3Fpfrom%3Dhome-topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egovernment%20sought%2C%20unsuccessfully%2C%20to%20allay%20these%20fears%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarmers'%20Other%20Demands%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20the%20farmers%20also%20want%20debt%20waivers%2C%20no%20hike%20in%20electricity%20tariffs%2C%20and%20withdrawal%20of%20police%20cases%20filed%20in%20the%202020%2F21%20protests%2C%20when%20they%20had%20violent%20clashes%20with%20security%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20they%20also%20want%20justice%20for%20farmers%20killed%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%2C%20reinstatement%20of%20the%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%2C%20and%20compensation%20to%20the%20families%20of%20those%20who%20died%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20Are%20The%20Farmers%20Now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtesting%20farmers%20are%20now%20camped%20around%202