rst%20Time%20Since%201947%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20since%20Independence%2C%20the%20national%20flag%20was%20unfurled%20in%20Puvarti%20-%20a%20village%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Sukma%20where%20the%20Maoists%20once%20ran%20a%20parallel%20government.%20A%20police%20camp%20was%20also%20set%20up%20by%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20which%20they%20believe%20will%20break%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20Maoists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPuvarti%2C%20on%20the%20border%20of%20Sukma%20and%20Bijapur%20districts%2C%20is%20the%20native%20village%20of%20Hidma%2C%20a%20self-styled%20commander%20of%20the%20banned%20guerrilla%20group%2C%20and%20his%20successor%20Barsa%20Deva.%20It%20is%20here%20that%20the%20Maoists%20strategized%20against%20the%20security%20forces%20and%20planned%20their%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%2C%20which%20had%20a%20pond%20and%20farms%2C%20had%20security%20arrangements%20required%20to%20confront%20any%20security%20team%2C%20found%20officials%20from%20the%20CRPF%20and%20state%20police%20during%20their%20inspection%20on%20Sunday.%20There%20were%20installations%20from%20where%20they%20could%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20passers-by.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20rest%20house%20that%20once%20served%20as%20a%20school%20stood%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20village.%20The%20land%20around%20it%2C%20where%20the%20Maoists%20grew%20vegetables%2C%20has%20also%20been%20taken%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vast%20area%20spanning%20kilometres%20used%20to%20be%20Maoist%20training%20camps%2C%20where%20they%20also%20held%20meetings%20and%20recruited%20young%20villagers%20living%20in%20nearby%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20provided%20an%20insight%20into%20how%20the%20banned%20group%20functioned%20and%20carried%20out%20heinous%20attacks%20on%20security%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opening%20of%20a%20security%20camp%20in%20the%20village%20delivers%20a%20severe%20blow%20to%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20Maoists.%20In%20an%20ar