led-in-maoist-stronghold-for-first-time-since-1947-5086396%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20China's%20budget-friendly%20answer%20to%20Apple's%20Vision%20Pro%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708333178000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107817546%2Cimgsize-252346.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fchinas-budget-friendly-answer-to-apples-vision-pro%2Farticleshow%2F107817546.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shenzhen-based%20company%20EmdoorVR%20has%20introduced%20the%20Vision%20SE%2C%20an%20affordable%20alternative%20to%20Apple's%20Vision%20Pro%20mixed-reality%20headset.%20Priced%20at%20less%20than%20%24280%2C%20the%20Vision%20SE%20lacks%20certain%20features%20but%20offers%20VR%20and%20AR%20viewing%20capabilities.%20EmdoorVR%20aims%20to%20penetrate%20the%20consumer%20segment%20with%20its%20headset.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fchinas-budget-friendly-answer-to-apples-vision-pro%2Farticleshow%2F107817546.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pic%20Of%20Passenger%20Sitting%20Right%20Behind%20Flyer%20On%20Empty%20Plane%20Sparks%20Debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20travelling%20on%20a%20plane%2C%20passengers%20should%20follow%20some%20basic%20etiquette%20and%20do%20their%20best%20to%20not%20disturb%20or%20trouble%20anyone%20seated%20around%20them.%20However%2C%20recently%20a%20plane%20passenger%20in%20the%20United%20States%20was%20left%20fuming%20when%20another%20passenger%20sat%20directly%20behind%20him%20on%20their%20almost%20empty%20Southwest%20flight.%20Taking%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Washington-based%20chef%2C%20Anthony%20Thomas%2C%20shared%20his%20ordeal%20along%20with%20a%20selfie%2C%20which%20showed%20a%20man%20sitting%20right%20behind%20him%20on%20an%20almost%20empty%20plane.%20%26quot%3BImagine%20having%20the%20luxury%20of%20boarding%20a%20flight%20with%20only%20two%20passengers%20on%20it.%20Of%20all%20the%20seats%20on%20the%20flight%2C%20%C2%A0look%20where%20he%20decided%20to%20sit%2C%20Mr%20Thomas%20captioned%20the%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%20a%20look%20below%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EImagine%20having%20the%20luxury%20of%20boarding%20a%20flight%20with%20only%20two%20passengers%20on%20it.%20Of%20all%20the%20seats%20on%20the%20flight%2C%20look%20where%20he%20decided%20to%20sit.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqluJhDUHBy%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqluJhDUHBy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Chef%20Anthony%20Thomas%20(%40ChefAnthonyDC)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChefAnthonyDC%2Fstatus%2F1757544261090787793%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2013%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20Mr%20Thomas'%20post%20has%20accumulated%20more%20than%2037%20million%20views.%20The%20tweet%20has%20also%20sparked%20a%20debate%20on%20airplane%20etiquette%20and%20personal%20space%20in%20the%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20same%20dude%20that%20won't%20skip%20the%2030%20empty%20urinals%20to%20snuggle%20up%20and%20try%20to%20talk%20while%20it's%20business%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20user%20commented.%20%26quot%3BI%20would've%20moved%2C%20honestly.%20Dude%20is%20weird%20and%20I%20wouldn't%20want%20him%20behind%20me%20just%20for%20that%20reason%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20users%20also%20believed%20that%20the%20man's%20behaviour%20was%20odd%2C%20given%20how%20empty%20the%20plane%20was%2C%20while%20others%20were%20not%20so%20quick%20to%20take%20Mr%20Thomas'%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20matter%20my%20friend.%20Recline%20allllll%20the%20way%20back.%20That's%20his%20fault%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20user.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20counting%205%20passengers%20total%20bud%20but%20yes%20he%20should%20find%20another%20seat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fintuitive-machines-moon-lander-captures-stunning-shot-of-earth-see-pics-5084674%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Intuitive%20Machines'%20Moon%20Lander%20Captures%20Stunning%20Shot%20Of%20Earth.%20See%20Pics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20one%20user%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BGuy's%20probably%20scared%20of%20flying%20instead%20of%20being%20super%20creep%20just%20ask%20him%20to%20sit%20in%20same%20row%20maybe%20you%20will%20make%20a%20friend%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20another%20expressed%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20sorry%20but%20if%20I%20board%20an%20empty%20flight%20im%20not%20sitting%20by%20myself%20either..%20thats%20creepy%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20go%20to%20my%20assigned%20seat%20before%20I%20start%20looking%20for%20an%20empty%20one%20that%20might%20be%20more%20comfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Ftravel%2Fnews-and-advice%2Fsouthwest-passenger-plane-seat-anthony-thomas-b2498359.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20flight%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20Southwest%20plane%2C%20which%20operates%20an%20open%20seating%20policy.%20This%20means%20that%20travellers%20flying%20with%20the%20airline%20can%20pick%20any%20open%20seat%20once%20they%20board%20their%20aircraft%20in%20their%20group%20number.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20a%20social%20media%20post%20has%20sparked%20a%20discussion%20on%20airplane%20etiquette.%20Earlier%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fpic-showing-plane-passengers-