rt%20and%20value-conscious%20housewife%2C%20and%20through%20her%2C%20it%20helped%20Surf%20pitch%20against%20Nirma%20while%20not%20playing%20the%20price%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20content%20and%20media%20overdose%20times%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20envision%20a%20single%20fictional%20advertising-led%20character%20reaching%20such%20cult%20status%20(there%20are%20a%20few%2C%20of%20course%2C%20like%20Swiggy%E2%80%99s%20Gulab%20Jamun%20Uncle)%2C%20but%20in%20those%20Doordarshan-only%20days%2C%20Lalita%20Ji%20was%20truly%20a%20phenomenon!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20way%2C%20you%20could%20say%20that%20HUL%E2%80%99s%20Surf%20was%20responding%20to%20Nirma%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Hema%2C%20Rekha%2C%20Jaya%20aur%20Sushma%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20famous%201982%20TV%20ad%20starring%20Sangeeta%20Bijlani.%20If%20Nirma%20was%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Esabki%20pasand%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%2C%20why%20would%20a%20woman%20(in%20those%20days%2C%20when%20washing%20powders%20were%20the%20exclusive%20domain%20of%20women!)%20choose%20Surf%2C%20which%20was%20priced%20higher%20than%20Nirma%3F%20Surf%20answered%20through%20the%20voice%20of%20Lalita%20Ji%2C%20a%20discerning%20and%20value-conscious%20housewife%20who%20got%20exasperated%20(%E2%80%9CBhaisaab!!%E2%80%9D)%20at%20the%20voiceover%20for%20not%20understanding%20the%20basics%20of%20getting%20the%20best%20value%20for%20the%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20later%2C%20in%201989%2C%20Nirma%20responded%20too%2C%20making%20it%20a%20long-running%20conversation%20between%20Nirma%20and%20HUL.%20But%20the%20turf%20was%20not%20washing%20powders%2C%20but%20washing%20soaps%2C%20where%20HUL%E2%80%99s%20Rin%20was%20pitted%20against%20Nirma%20Super%20detergent%20soap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20Lalita%20Ji%2C%20Deepika%20Ji%20%E2%80%93%20played%20by%20%3Cem%3ERamayan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20%E2%80%98Sita%E2%80%99%2C%20Deepika%20Chikhlia%20%E2%80%93%20gets%20down%20from%20her%20car%2C%20and%20walks%20into%20a%20store%2C%20ready%20to%20pick%20up%20her%20readily-packed%20monthly%20groceries.%20When%20she%20sees%20that%20the%20shopkeeper%20had%20placed%20a%20costlier%20detergent%20soap%20bar%20in%20her%20basket%2C%20she%20asks%20for%20Nirma%20Super%2C%20specifically%2C%20with%20the%20logic%20that%20if%20it%20gave%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20whiteness%20and%20foam%20at%20a%20much%20lower%20price%2C%20why%20would%20she%20buy%20a%20costlier%20detergent%20soap%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgPd5NwdkUpY%3Fsi%3DhnlLzDWiKj8J6QzC%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20Alyque%20Padamsee%20had%20famously%20mentioned%20that%20he%20modeled%20Lalita%20Ji%20after%20his%20own%20mother%2C%20who%20would%20get%20down%20from%20a%20Mercedes%20that%20costs%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20(in%20those%20days)%20and%20haggle%20with%20a%20vegetable%20vendor%20for%20Rs%202!%20Why%3F%20Because%2C%20%E2%80%98there%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20buying%20something%20cheap%20and%20buying%20something%20good%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20Lalita%20Ji%20went%20on%20to%20complete%20in%20the%20Surf%20ad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Chaudhary%2C%20a%20graduate%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20National%20School%20of%20Drama%2C%20the%20ad%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20even%20led%20to%20a%20Doordarshan%20series%2C%20%3Cem%3EUdaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20she%20played%20the%20inspirational%20role%20of%20IPS%20officer%20Kalyani%20Singh.%20The%20title%20music%20of%20%3Cem%3EUdaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20composed%20by%20Shaarang%20Dev%2C%20may%20still%20ring%20a%20bell%20or%20two%20for%20%E2%80%9980s%20kids!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fgw6DMiR0tR4%3Fsi%3Dh-8cbI2vEnLtp7SL%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20in%20the%20limelight%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98Lalita%20Ji%E2%80%99%20character%20has%20probably%20been%20long%20forgotten%20already.%20But%20the%20news%20of%20her%20passing%20away%20made%20me%20pause%20and%20reminisce%20about%20the%20%E2%80%98good%20old%20Doordarshan%E2%80%99%20times%20and%20the%20endlessly%20innocent%20days%20of%20growing%20up%20in%20Srirangam%2C%20near%20Trichy%2C%20when%20the%20television%20set%20first%20came%20to%20our%20house%2C%20and%20along%20with%20it%2C%20the%20magic%20of%20Doordarshan%E2%80%A6%20and%20Lalita%20Ji!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20only%20one%20television%20channel%20and%20the%20entire%20country%20watched%20it%20together%2C%20forming%20a%20monoculture%20that%20united%20all%20of%20us%20together.%20We%20discussed%20the%20same%20TV%20stars%2C%20same%20TV%20ads%20and%20the%20same%20TV%20programmes.%20And%20Lalita%20Ji%20was%20the%20same%20value-conscious%20housewife%20we%20all%20loved%20emulating%20together%2C%20as%20a%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMay%20Kavita%20%E2%80%98Lalita%20Ji%E2%80%99%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20soul%20rest%20in%20peace.%20Om%20Shanti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKarthik%20Srinivasan%20is%20a%20communications%20strategy%20consultant.%20He%20tweets%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbeastoftraal%5C%22%3E%40beastoftraal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708331526000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F19140019%2FScreenshot-2024-02-19-at-2.00.07-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fremembering-kavita-chaudhary-and-her-lalita-ji-that-bound-a-nation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20Do