0of%20Police%20Shatrujeet%20Kapur%20has%20denied%20that%20the%20use%20of%20pellet%20guns%20against%20farmers%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20their%20way%20to%20Delhi%2C%20and%20have%20been%20stopped%20at%20at%20least%20two%20locations%20%E2%80%93%20Khanauri%20and%20Shambhu%20Border.%20Kapur%20said%20that%20the%20police%20are%20using%20%E2%80%9Cminimum%20force%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fharyana-dgp-denies-using-pellet-guns-against-protesting-farmers%2Farticle67860605.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20has%20shown%20that%20multiple%20farmers%20have%20been%20admitted%20to%20hospital%20because%20of%20injuries%20they%20faced%20during%20police%20action.%20Farmers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fpakistan-india-farmer-shambhu-medical-cost%5C%22%3Ehave%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20injuries%20were%20caused%20by%20pellet%20guns%20and%20tear%20gas%20shells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20use%20of%20pellet%20guns%20against%20protesters%2C%20Kapur%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20the%20SOP%20being%20followed%20by%20the%20police%20is%20to%20first%20use%20tear%20gas%2C%20then%20water%20cannons%2C%20cane%20charge%20and%20lastly%20rubber%20bullets%20are%20fired%20from%20a%20distance%20of%2050-60%20yards.%20The%20rubber%20bullets%20are%20not%20aimed%20directly%20at%20the%20mob%2C%20they%20are%20pointed%20to%20the%20ground%20which%20ricochet%20and%20then%20hit%20the%20target.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20to%20injure%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20follow-up%20question%20on%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20metal%20shrapnel%20in%20farmers%E2%80%99%20bodies%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20not%20come%20across%20photographs%20or%20reports%20in%20newspapers%20of%20pellet%20gun%20injuries.%20Our%20response%20is%20limited%20to%20rubber%20bullets.%20This%20is%20a%20differen