h%20Hygenco%20to%20understand%20the%20need%20for%20green%20hydrogen%20and%20how%20it%20will%20ensure%20a%20sustainable%20future%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20India%20needs%20green%20hydrogen%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20pursuing%20engineering%20in%202005%2C%20Amit%20completed%20his%20higher%20studies%20in%20business%20administration%20at%20Shailesh%20J%20Mehta%20School%20of%20Management%2C%20IIT-Bombay%20in%202010.%20He%20commenced%20his%20career%20as%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Vivaan%20Solar%2C%20a%20leading%20solar%20plant%20installation%20company%20offering%20turnkey%20solar%20power%20plants%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-3-1707917516.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hygenco%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20construct%20and%20operate%20a%20100%20percent%20green%20hydrogen%20plant%20in%20Maharashtra.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-3-1707917516.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-3-1707917516-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-3-1707917516-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-3-1707917516-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-3-1707917516-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341882%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHygenco%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20construct%20and%20operate%20a%20100%20percent%20green%20hydrogen%20plant%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20in%20the%20renewable%20energy%20sector%2C%20Amit%20wanted%20to%20work%20towards%20addressing%20India%E2%80%99s%20energy%20crises.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20a%20fast-growing%20country%2C%20which%20is%20also%20increasing%20the%20use%20of%20fossil%20fuels.%20Since%20the%20country%20is%20significantly%20dependent%20on%20imports%20for%20its%20energy%20needs%2C%20there%20is%20a%20very%20strong%20business%20sense%20for%20harnessing%20the%20power%20of%20green%20hydrogen%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%2039-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20why%20India%20needs%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20the%20major%20factors%20why%20we%20feel%20India%20needs%20green%20hydrogen%20include%2C%20energy%20independence%2C%20achieving%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20net%20zero%20targets%2C%20and%20creating%20huge%20job%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20save%20our%20forex.%20The%20precious%20foreign%20exchange%20saved%20by%20reducing%20fossil%20fuel%20imports%20can%20be%20harnessed%20for%20social%20use%20such%20as%20health%20and%20education.%20Further%2C%20the%20country%20can%20even%20target%20to%20become%20a%20net%20exporter%20of%20ammonia%20and%20its%20derivatives%20from%20being%20a%20large%20importer%20of%20fossil%20fuels%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20Amit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGreen%20hydrogen%20and%20its%20derivatives%20as%20fuel%20can%20decarbonise%20hard-to-abate%20sectors%2C%20especially%20since%20these%20sectors%20contribute%20nearly%2080%20percent%20of%20carbon%20footprint.%20This%20will%20be%20crucial%20as%20conventional%20electricity%20replacement%20by%20100%20percent%20green%20electricity%20will%20only%20result%20in%2020%20percent%20decarbonisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20the%20most%20of%20a%20growing%20demand%20for%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20Amit%20launched%20Hygenco%20in%202020%20with%20a%20vision%20to%20help%20India%20achieve%20energy