hip%20might%20prove%20a%20solution.%20This%20was%20backed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20that%20held%20that%20living%20together%20as%20partners%20without%20getting%20married%20is%20not%20illegal%20or%20a%20criminal%20offence.%20Thus%2C%20Happy%20Seniors%20was%20born%20in%20Pune%20in%202012%20on%20the%20precipice%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328138%2Fmadurai-dr-swaminathan-doctor-on-wheels-takes-affordable-healthcare-to-senior-citizens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelping%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20find%20love%20in%20their%20old%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20modern%20spin%20on%20companionship%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhav%20Damle%E2%80%99s%20model%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20does%20not%20have%20any%20loopholes%3B%20he%20has%20seen%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20main%20reason%20why%20these%20kinds%20of%20relationships%20are%20frowned%20upon%20among%20youngsters%20is%20because%20of%20the%20possibility%20of%20children.%20Whose%20responsibility%20will%20the%20children%20be%20if%20there%20is%20no%20marriage%20in%20place%3F%20But%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20senior%20citizens%2C%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20%5Bmuch%5D%20scope%20for%20this%20problem%20to%20arise.%20Their%20children%20are%20settled%20in%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20all%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323097%2Fpune-man-starts-yodda-elder-care-startup-for-emergency-help-to-senior-citizens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esenior%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20has%20assisted%20in%20finding%20the%20right%20partner%20are%20financially%20stable.%20In%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20property%20disputes%20do%20not%20arise%20as%20there%20is%20no%20legal%20binding%20between%20the%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20Happy%20Seniors%20beg