0been%20single%20for%20over%2025%20years%2C%20she%20was%20reluctant%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20finding%20love%20again.%20Debarti%20encouraged%20her%20to%20just%20befriend%20Swapan%20and%20proceed%20as%20per%20her%20wish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThings%20progressed%20positively.%20Swapan%20is%20amazing%20and%20my%20mom%20got%20along%20beautifully%20with%20him.%20He%20accepted%20her%20with%20all%20his%20heart%2C%20and%20now%20showers%20her%20with%20all%20the%20love%20she%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Debarti%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3ESheThePeople%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Finally%2C%20in%20March%202022%2C%20the%20duo%20got%20married%2C%20and%20Debarti%20found%20a%20father%20and%20the%20family%20she%20craved%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20just%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20world%20that%20just%20like%20parents%20do%20their%20best%20for%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20happiness%2C%20similarly%2C%20children%20are%20equally%20responsible%20for%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335353%2Fharish-closepet-masterchef-india-father-cooking-school-lunchbox%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparents%E2%80%99%20happiness%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20feel%20lucky%20that%20I%20got%20the%20opportunity%20to%20help%20my%20mother%20get%20her%20happiness%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3ESheThePeople%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20%E2%80%98Finally%2C%20I%20married%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20400px)%20100vw%2C%20400px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fatul-suhashni-1707910869.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Suhasini%20Mulay%20found%20her%20husband%20Atul%20Gurtu%20when%20she%20was%2059%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fatul-suhashni-1707910869.jp