he%20rooms%2C%20they%20are%20named%20after%20avatars%20of%20Lord%20Vishnu.%20The%20idea%20is%20for%20people%20to%20understand%20the%20history%20of%20Sawantwadi.%20When%20you%20enter%20a%20certain%20room%2C%20everything%20from%20the%20doorknob%20to%20the%20decor%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F90205%2F10-sustainable-homestays-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20of%20our%20artisans%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20%3Cem%3Eganjifa%3C%2Fem%3E%20symbols%20painted%20on%20them.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20inculcated%20the%20art%20in%20bits%20and%20pieces%20in%20the%20night%20lamps%2C%20the%20tea%20trays%20and%20everywhere%20we%20could%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20this%20is%20fascinating%2C%20Shraddha%20says%20you%20should%20hear%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20furniture.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20have%20been%20made%20by%20the%20Sawant%20Bhonsle%20family%20in%20their%20unit%20%E2%80%98Sawantwadi%20Lacquerwares%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20this%20is%20also%20the%20place%20where%20the%20%3Cem%3Eganjifa%3C%2Fem%3E%20revival%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20grandfather-in-law%20HH%20Rajesaheb%20Shivramraje%20Bhonsle%20visited%20the%20Victoria%20and%20Albert%20Museum%20in%20London%2C%20he%20noticed%20a%20label%20reading%20Sawantwadi%20Cards.%20He%20and%20his%20wife%20learnt%20the%20art%20from%20the%2080-year-old%20artist%20Pundalik%20Chitari%20who%20at%20that%20time%20would%20make%20only%20two%20sets%20of%20%3Cem%3Eganjifa%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20year.%20They%20started%20Sawantwadi%20Lacquerwares%20in%201971%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338327%2Feco-village-khaama-kethna-in-goa-forests-run-by-lawyer-panta-ferrao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevive%20and%20promote%20the%20art%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%3Cem%3Eganjifa%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20lacquerware.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrue%20to%20the%20message%20championed%20by%20their%20ancestors%2C%20the%20couple%20is%20insistent%20on%20empowering%20the%20local%20artisanal%20communities%20through%20their%20creation%20of%20the%20boutique%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20only%20hired%20locals.%20We%E2%80%99re%20always%20told%20that%20the%20process%20would%20have%20been%20easier%20and%20quicker%20if%20we%20had%20employed%20architectural%20firms%20from%20bigger%20cities%2C%20but%20we%20were%20insistent%20that%20we%20wanted%20the%20locals%20to%20be%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20restoration%20from%20start%20to%20finish%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20couple%20is%20glad%20they%20opted%20for%20this.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20led%20us%20to%20discover%20so%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338515%2Fluv-shekawat-started-utsav-camp-sariska-tiger-reserve-sustainable-nature-retreat-alwar-rajasthan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einteresting%20facets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Shraddha%2C%20sharing%20an%20anecdote%20of%20how%20they%20came%20across%20huge%20stones%20while%20they%20were%20clearing%20the%20ground%20where%20the%20swimming%20pool%20currently%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20forest%20earlier.%20During%20the%20clearing%20spree%2C%20we%20began%20seeing%20mosaic%20patterns%20on%20the%20stones%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20realised%20these%20were%20actually%20tiles.%20Eventually%2C%20we%20came%20across%20the%20first%20%3Cem%3Ewada%3C%2Fem%3E%20our%20ancestors%20had%20built.%E2%80%9D%20Today%2C%20you%20will%20see%20those%20same%20stones%20in%20the%20boutique%20hotel%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fthe-sawantwadi-palace-4-1707824914.jpg%5C%22%20